      "speech": "WebページをJSで操作する仕組みだよ！",
      "background": "space",
      "title": "DOMって何？",
      "content": "DOMはHTMLをオブジェクトとして表現したもの。JSはこれを通じてページを書き換えられます！",
      "emoji": "🌐",
      "highlight": "DOM = HTMLのオブジェクト表現"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "lesson",
      "duration": 6000,
      "garuchanAnimation": "bounce",
      "speech": "HTMLの要素をJSで取得する方法！",
      "background": "forest",
      "title": "要素の取得",
      "content": "document.getElementById('id')、querySelector('.class')などで要素を取得！",
      "emoji": "🔍",
      "highlight": "getElementById / querySelector"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "lesson",
      "duration": 6000,
      "garuchanAnimation": "float",
      "speech": "取得した要素のテキストや内容を変えよう！",
      "background": "classroom",
      "title": "要素の変更",
      "content": "element.textContent = 'New text'でテキスト変更。innerHTML でHTMLごと変更！",
      "emoji": "✏️",
      "highlight": "textContent / innerHTML"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "lesson",
      "duration": 6000,
      "garuchanAnimation": "bounce",
      "speech": "新しい要素を追加したり削除したりできる！",
      "background": "city",
      "title": "要素の追加・削除",
      "content": "document.createElement('div')で作成、appendChild()で追加、remove()で削除！",
      "emoji": "➕",
      "highlight": "createElement / appendChild / remove"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "lesson",
      "duration": 6000,
      "garuchanAnimation": "float",
      "speech": "JSでCSSを動的に変更できるよ！",
      "background": "candy",
      "title": "スタイルの変更",
      "content": "element.style.color = 'red'でCSSをJS から設定！クラスの追加はclassList.add()！",
      "emoji": "🎨",
      "highlight": "style.color / classList.add"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "lesson",
      "duration": 6000,
      "garuchanAnimation": "bounce",
      "speech": "href、src、classなどの属性を操作しよう！",
      "background": "ocean",
      "title": "属性の操作",
      "content": "element.getAttribute('href')で取得、setAttribute('href','URL')で設定！",
      "emoji": "🏷️",
      "highlight": "getAttribute / setAttribute"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "lesson",
      "duration": 6000,
      "garuchanAnimation": "float",
      "speech": "親・子・兄弟の要素にアクセスする方法！",
      "background": "classroom",
      "title": "DOMの走査",
      "content": "parentNode、children、nextSiblingなどで要素ツリーを移動できます！",
      "emoji": "🌳",
      "highlight": "parentNode children nextSibling"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
